  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Ah, you have arrived at just the right moment. I am developing a new scroll, yet I find myself lacking the materials needed for my research. Might you lend me your strength?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "My thanks. What I require is a #b#t4000063##k. It carries a mysterious power, though it is difficult to handle—so for research of this scale, I need quite a large amount. Please, make haste."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Hm… I had hoped you would understand why I devote myself so deeply to this research…"
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Excellent. With this much, I believe I can continue my studies for some time. Your aid has been invaluable."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "I cannot allow such effort to go unrewarded. Please, take this #t2002010#. With it, you may find the path of Arcforge training a little easier."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Yet this is troubling… it seems far more #t4000063# will be required for this study than I first predicted. I suspect I will be calling on your help again. Until then, travel safely."
        }
      },
